Titolo: Dragon Quest Monsters: Joker 2

Anno: 2010

Descrizione: Dragon Quest Monsters: Joker 2 (ドラゴンクエストモンスターズ ジョーカー2, Doragon Kuesuto Monsutāzu Jōkā Tsu) is a Nintendo DS role-playing video game published by Square Enix. It is the sequel to Dragon Quest Monsters: Joker and is the fifth game in the Dragon Quest Monsters series. It was released in Japan on April 28, 2010, with a United States release on September 19, 2011, with a European release following on October 7, 2011. An expanded version of the game, titled Dragon Quest Monsters: Joker 2 Professional, was released on March 31, 2011. It features new monsters and abilities, with the same story.